machine_end_gcode:
G1 Z{z_offset+min(max_layer_z+10, printable_height)} F600 ; Move head up

G28 X ; home extruder on x-axis

M140 S0 ; turn off heatbed
M104 S0 ; turn off hotends
M107 ; turn off fan
M84 X Y E ; disable motors
machine_start_gcode:
M605 S2 X150 R{nozzle_temperature_initial_layer[1]-nozzle_temperature_initial_layer[0]} ; Initialize copy mode with X-offset and temp diff between extruders
M605 S3 ; Mirror Mode Start

G90 ; use absolute coordinates
M83 ; extruder relative mode
M413 S0 ; disable power-loss recovery

M140 S{bed_temperature_initial_layer[0]} ; start heating bed
M104 S{nozzle_temperature_initial_layer[0]-50} ; Start heating nozzles

G28 X ; home x to buckets

M190 S{bed_temperature_initial_layer[0]} ; wait for bed temp to stabilize

M280 P0 S160 ; Reset BL/CR Touch
G34 ; z stepper auto-align
G28 ; home all axis
G28 X ; home extruder on x-axis (to the buckets)
M109 S{nozzle_temperature_initial_layer[0]} ; Heat and wait for nozzle temps to stabilize
M420 S1 ; enable bed leveling

G1 Z2.0 F3000 ; Move Z Axis down near bed

G92 E0 ; Reset Extruder
G1 X0.5 Y20 Z0.3 F5000.0 ; Move to start position
G1 X0.5 Y200.0 Z0.3 F1500.0 E14 ; Draw the first line
G1 X1 Y200.0 Z0.3 F5000.0 ; Move to side a little
G1 X1 Y20 Z0.3 F1500.0 E14 ; Draw the second line

G1 Z2.0 F3000 ; Move Z Axis up little to prevent scratching of Heat Bed
G28 X ; home to bucket - wipe
name: SV04 Mirror Mode CHT 0.6mm
